<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>No spoilers here, please. <p>
NO SPOILERS HERE!</em></strong> 
</p>
<p>
The Polearmmaster is a Warrior who specializes in polearms. 
</p>
<p>
The training is so intense and specific that Polearmmasters gain huge bonuses when fighting with their chosen weapon, dependent on their Polearm-mastery skill. In most other respects they perform about as well as a generic Warrior. 
</p>
<p>
Starting stat modifiers, starting Skills, innate abilities and starting equipment: Please see the in-game help. 
</p>
